sign.text: Welcome!! Use your mouse pointer to click and drag a dotted line. If that line is white and not purple the Warlock will teleport to the opposite side of the line. The square marker on the end of your guide line will show where you will land.

Using your new teleporting powers try to follow the star tiles marked on the floor. Continue along the path and position the warlock on the end pad to finish the level and progress. If you get stuck press the "help (?)" icon in the top right for controls.
